Package org.apache.cxf.resource

Interface ResourceResolver

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BusApplicationContextResourceResolver, ClassLoaderResolver, ClasspathResolver, ObjectTypeResolver, PropertiesResolver, SinglePropertyResolver
    public interface ResourceResolver
    Resolves resource. A ResourceResolver is used to find references to resources that are being injected into classes
